# Review

Ask the user which review to run with the host's native question tool. In Claude Code call `AskUserQuestion`. In Codex call `request_user_input`. In Cursor call `AskQuestion`. When none is available, ask in plain text. Provide exactly one single-select question with two options:

- `bugbot`: bug-focused review ([review-bugbot/SKILL.md](../review-bugbot/SKILL.md))
- `security`: security-focused review ([review-security/SKILL.md](../review-security/SKILL.md))

After the user chooses, run the matching review once:

- Bug-focused: follow [review-bugbot/SKILL.md](../review-bugbot/SKILL.md).
- Security-focused: follow [review-security/SKILL.md](../review-security/SKILL.md).
